<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%= title %> – Kishore Orthopedic Centre</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

  <main>
    <!-- Page Hero -->
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <span class="section-tag">Our Story</span>
        <h1>About Kishore Orthopedic Centre</h1>
        <p>Two decades of healing, growing, and caring for the communities we serve.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Mission -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="about-story">
          <div class="about-story__text">
            <span class="section-tag">Our Mission</span>
            <h2>Restoring Lives, One Patient at a Time</h2>
            <p>Founded in 2005 by Dr. K. Srinivas Kishore, Kishore Orthopedic Centre began with a simple but powerful vision — to bring world-class orthopedic care to every patient, regardless of their background.</p>
            <p>What started as a small clinic with a big heart has grown into one of Hyderabad's most trusted orthopedic institutions, with a team of 15+ specialists, state-of-the-art facilities and a legacy of over 10,000 successful treatments.</p>
            <p>We are driven by compassion, guided by evidence-based medicine and committed to making every patient feel heard, respected and cared for throughout their journey back to health.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-story__visual">
            <div class="about-visual-card">
              <div class="about-icon-large">🏥</div>
              <h3>Kishore Orthopedic Centre</h3>
              <p>Hyderabad's Trusted Choice for Orthopedic Excellence</p>
              <div class="about-badges">
                <span class="about-badge">NABH Accredited</span>
                <span class="about-badge">ISO Certified</span>
                <span class="about-badge">Award Winning</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Values -->
    <section class="section section-alt">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-tag">Our Values</span>
          <h2>What Drives Everything We Do</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-4">
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">❤️</div>
            <h3>Compassion</h3>
            <p>We treat every patient with the warmth and empathy we would want for our own family members.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">🎯</div>
            <h3>Excellence</h3>
            <p>We continuously raise the bar on surgical outcomes, patient experience and clinical standards.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">🤝</div>
            <h3>Integrity</h3>
            <p>Honest, transparent communication and ethical practice are the foundation of every patient relationship.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">🔬</div>
            <h3>Innovation</h3>
            <p>We embrace the latest medical advances to offer our patients safer, faster and more effective treatments.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Milestones -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-tag">Our Journey</span>
          <h2>Milestones That Define Us</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline">
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-year">2005</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h3>Founded</h3>
              <p>Dr. K. Srinivas Kishore established the centre with 3 doctors and a mission to provide accessible, expert orthopedic care.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-year">2010</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h3>NABH Accreditation</h3>
              <p>Received prestigious NABH accreditation, cementing our commitment to the highest standards of patient safety and quality.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-year">2015</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h3>Advanced Surgical Suite</h3>
              <p>Opened our fully-equipped advanced surgical suite with robotic assistance capabilities and 3D imaging systems.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-year">2020</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h3>Sports Medicine Department</h3>
              <p>Launched a dedicated sports medicine and performance rehabilitation department, becoming the preferred centre for athletes.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-year">2025</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h3>10,000 Patients Milestone</h3>
              <p>Celebrated the treatment of our 10,000th patient — a testament to the trust our community places in us.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Accreditations -->
    <section class="section section-alt">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-tag">Accreditations & Awards</span>
          <h2>Recognised for Excellence</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="accreditation-grid">
          <div class="accreditation-card">
            <div class="accreditation-icon">🏆</div>
            <h4>Best Orthopedic Hospital</h4>
            <p>Hyderabad Healthcare Awards 2023</p>
          </div>
          <div class="accreditation-card">
            <div class="accreditation-icon">✅</div>
            <h4>NABH Accredited</h4>
            <p>National Accreditation Board for Hospitals</p>
          </div>
          <div class="accreditation-card">
            <div class="accreditation-icon">🌟</div>
            <h4>ISO 9001:2015 Certified</h4>
            <p>Quality Management Systems</p>
          </div>
          <div class="accreditation-card">
            <div class="accreditation-icon">🎖️</div>
            <h4>Excellence in Patient Care</h4>
            <p>Telangana Medical Council 2022</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
